  Chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 khoaN3-hoat , khiok si7 hou7 lang5 khah ai3 pi-koan iam3-se3 . se3-kan ban7-hang7 sit8-chai7 put-si5 teh pian3-chhian, chong2-si7 bo5 tek-khak long2 si7 pian3-phaiN2. Chiau3 goa2 khoaN3 , sui-jian5 si7 koh khah an2-choan2 pian3, kau3-boe2 tiaN7-tioh8 si7 pian3-ho2 . Na7-si7 kong2 kiu3-keng3 e5 tai7-chi3 si7 bi5-biau2 hou7 lang5 oh-tit toan3 ; na7-si7 an2-ni , goa2 iau2 e7 thang kong2 chit8-ku3, lang5 tiaN7-tioh8 si7 hi-bong7 se3-kan pian3-chiaN5 ho2, tek-khak si7 bo5 sim-goan7 hoaN-hi2 se3-kan pian3-cho3 phaiN2. Si7 , se3-kan put-si5 ti7-teh pian3, chong2-si7 lang5 tiaN7-tioh8 si7 ai3 se3-kan pian3 ho2; ban7-it na7 pian3 phaiN2, cho3 lang5 tek-khak kan-khou2 , au2-nau2, pun5 toa7-khui3. 
  Se3-kan ban7-hang7 teh pian3-oaN7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 khe-chui2 ti7-teh lau5. Li2 khoaN3 , khe-chui2 oan-oan ti7-teh lau5, me5-jit8 to long2 bo5 u7 chhun3-khek e5 hioh-khun3. Chong2-si7 m7-thang kong2 , Khe-chui2 si7 it-khi3 bo5 hoe5-thau5. Tioh8 , khe-chui2 si7 tui3 soaN-teng2 lau5--loh8-lai5, tit8-thau3 lau5 tui3 hai2-nih khi3. ChhiaN2 siuN7-khoaN3 , khe-chui2 na7-si7 it-khi3 bo5 hoe5-thau5, soaN-teng2 choaN2-iuN7 u7 hiah che7 e5 chui2 put-si5 to lau5 be7 liau2? Sit8-chai7 khe-chui2 m7-si7 it-khi3 bo5 hoe5-thau5 ; khe-chui2 lau5 kau3 hai2-nih e5 tiong-kan, tioh8 siu7 jit8-thau5 phak8-sio , tui3 an2-ni chui2 to7 pian3-cho3 chui2-ian chheng3-chiuN7 thiN-teng2 khi3. Chui2-ian ti7 thiN-teng2 kiN3-tioh8 leng2-hong, chiu7 koh pian3-chiaN5 chui2 ka-lauh8 tui3 soaN-teng2 te7-bin7 lai5, che chiu7-si7 kio3-choe3 hou7 . Sou2-i2 thang chai , khe-chui2 si7 tui3 soaN-teng2 lau5-loh8 hai2, chong2-si7 kau3 hai2 e7 koh chheng3-chiuN7 soaN , si7 an2-ni sun5-hoan5 teh-tng2 . se3-kan ban7-hang7 teh pian3-oaN7 , khoaN3-chin to chiau3 chit e5 khoan2;si7 u7 chiau3 it-teng7 e5 lou7-keng3 teh pian3-chhian, tek-khak m7-si7 bo5 tiaN7-tioh8 loan7-loan7 ti7-teh ka2. Chui2 tioh8 kiaN5 lau5, tioh8 pian3-oaN7 chiah be7 chhau3, se3-kan ban7-hang7 ia7-si7 tioh8-ai3 ke2-ku7 oaN7-sin chiah e7 u7 chin3-pou7 . Chui2 sui-jian5 si7 chin chheng chin ho2 , m7-ku2 na7-si7 put-si5 chek ti7 chit8 sou2-chai7 , bo5 loa7-ku2 chiu7 e7 pian3 lo5 hoat chhau3-bi7 . 
  Se3-kan sui-jian5 si7 koh-khah ho2 e5 tai7-chi3, na7 m7-si7 e7 thang kap si5-se3 peN5-peN5 lai5 pian3-oaN7 , bo5 loa7-ku2 ia7 tek-khak tioh8 ai3 chiaN5-cho3 ku7-siuN3 bo5 hap8-eng7 e5 mih8. Se3-kan e5 teh pian3-chhian tu2-tu2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 khe-chui2 teh lau5, mi5-jit8 to long2 bo5 hioh-khun3; chui2 ju2-lau5 si7 ju2-oah8 ju2 chheng-khi3 , se3-kan sia7-hoe7 ju2 pian3 si7 ju2 sin ju2 chin3-pou7 . Chui2 teh lau5 u7 chiau3 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 hoat-tou7 , se3-kan ban7-hang7 e5 pian3-chhian ia7-si7 u7 it-teng7 e5 chhu3-su7 , tek-khak bo5 hit-ho7 ah-nng7 ko7 tui3 chioh8-thau5-phang7 chhut-lai5 e5 tai7-chi3. 
  2. Tai5-oan5 u7 pian3 a2-si7 bo5
  Chiau3 bak8-chiu sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 lai5 kong2, chit ji7-chap8 goa7 ni5 lai5, Tai5-oan5 si7 pian3 chin-che7. Khah-cha2 lang5 teh kau-thong ong2-lai5 long2 si7 eng7 kha kiaN5, u7-tiok8 e5 lang5 si7 che7-kio7 khia5-be2. TaN kau3 to2-loh8 to si7 u7 hoe2-chhia, chu7-choan2-chhia, chu7-tong7-chhia thang che7. Chai5-cheng5 khah gau5--e5 chit8-jit8 ia7-si7 be7 kiaN5-koe3 chap8-phou3 lou7, chong2-si7 hian7-si5 chit8-jit8 beh chau2 chit8-pah-goa7 phou3 (10 li2 ), si7 iong7-iN7. Cha2 e5 to7-lou7 ke-lou7 long2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 ke-tng5-a2 oan-oan oat-oat chin se3-tiau5; hian7-si5 to long2 si7 chin tit8, chin khoah, chin toa7-tiau5, chin peN5-thaN2. Cheng5 ke-lou7 e5 chui2-kau khah bo5 thong, sou2-i2 chhau3-chui2 chek kui-khut , ti3-kau3 seN bang2 seN thang5, hoat tok8-khi3, hou7 lang5 khoai3 phoa3-peN7, hian7-kim tai7-khai3 ke-chhi7 long2 u7 khui chui2-kau, si3-ke3 to long2 ta-sang. Eng2-tang-si5 long2 si7 eng7 chhau3-iu5 teh tiam2-teng, m7-na7 si7 bo5 kau3 kng , sit8-chai7 chin gui5-hiam2, chin kau7 ou-ian; chong2-si7 chit-tiap8 i2-keng u7 tian7-teng thang tiam2, am3-si5 e7 thang chio3 pi2 jit8-si5 koh-khah kng. Kok sou2-chai7 ke-chhi7 ke chin sui2, ia7 u7 ke siat kong-hng5 thang thit-tho5, ia7 u7 chin-che7 toa7-keng e5 chhu3 thang khoaN3. Che7-che7 sou2-chai7 u7 toa7-keng e5 che3-thng5 hoe7-sia7 , ki-khi3 e5 siaN khin3-khong3-hau2; cho3 seng-li2 e5 hoat-tou7 ia7 long2 kap cheng5 u7 koh-iuN7; hak8-hau7 ia7 u7 khah cheng2-tun3 khah che7 keng; cho3 koaN e5 lang5 ia7 si7 ke khah-che7 khah-giam5 , chhu2-chhat8-a2 kiam2 chin-che7 , kiong5-kong3-chhat8 e7 thang kong2 si7 i2-keng cheh8-cheng2 liau2. 
  Theh8 hian7-chai7 e5 Tai5-oan5 lai5 pi2-kau3 eng2-pai2, u7 pian3-chhian e5 sou2-chai7 si7 chin-che7 . Iah8 sou2 u7 pian3-liau2 e5 si7 ho2-phaiN2 chham-chhi, khiok m7-si7 long2-chong2 thang kiong-hi2. Ho2-phaiN2 chhiaN2 bo5-lun7 , kan-ta chhiaN2 siuN7-khoaN3 chiah e5 sou2 u7 pian3-oaN7 e5 tiam2 si7 tui3 an2-choaN2 lai5? Put-lun7 hou7 siaN2 lang5 kong2, phah-sng3 kaN2 bo5 lang5 beh kong2 si7 tui3 lan2 Pun2-to2-lang5 e5 sim-lai7 kek chhut-lai5, a2-si7 tui3 lan2 e5 chhiu2 lai5 cho7-chiaN5. Kian3-siau3 ah! Lan2 m7-na7 be7-hiau2-tit ka-ti7 kek-chhut chit ho7 , lian5 oh8 lang5 , toe3 lang5 e5 khoan2-iuN7 lan2 to si7 be7-e7. Siat-su2 mai3-tit pat8-lang5 kap lan2 chhap, chiong hian7-si5 chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 to2-lai7 sou2 u7 it-chhe3 e5 si-siat tak8-hang7 e5 ki-koan pang3 hou7 lan2 lai5 chiang2 , lan2 bo5 chai5-tiau7 thang chiang2-li2 ho2-se3 , che si7 khoaN3 hian7-hian7 e5 su7, phah-sng3 m7-bian2 loa7-ku2 e7 the3 kau3 kap it-ji7-chap8 ni5 cheng5 sio-siang7. 
  M7-si7 goa2 ai3 bu2-jiok8 ka-ti7 , sit8-chai7 si7 chit-e5 khoan2, ka-ti7 o-lo2 to ia7 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7. Sou2-i2 tioh8 beng5-pek8; Tai5-oan5 sui-jian5 si7 u7 pian3-chhian, che si7 lang5 cho3 hou7 lan2--e5, m7-si7 chhut chu7 lan2 e5 chai5-tiau7. Tui3 an2-ni tioh8 kong2, “Tai5-oan5 si7 bo5 pian3 khah tioh8 .” Se3-kan si5-si5 teh pian3 , pat8-lang5 khek-khek long2 u7 teh oaN7-sin , chong2-si7 lan2 iau2-ku2 si7 chiau3 ji7-saN-chap8 ni5 cheng5 e5 thau5-bin7. In-ui7 an2-ni tai7-ke tioh8 pi2 eng2-pai2 khah kan-khou2 , khah bo5 chhu3-bi7 si7 eng-kai. Ai5--ah! Tai5-oan5 u7 pian3-sin , chong2-si7 tai7-ke to si7 ju2 kio3 khou2! Sin--e5 si7 m7-bat, ku7--e5 iu7 si7 chha-put-to teh-beh be7-ki3-tit. Bak8-chiu kim-kim khoaN3 pat8-lang5 phiau-phiau-phiat-phiat teh oah8-tang7, m7-ku2 ka-ti7 chhin-chhiuN7 phoaN3-peN7-lang5 ; ai3 beh toe3 lang5 tio5 kha si7 khia7 be7 chai7, beh oh8 lang5 pi2 chhiu2 iu7 kiah8 be7 khi2; siuN7 beh than3 lang5 e5 chhui3-boe2 chhiuN3 , m7-ku2 na5-au5 ta-ta, chhui3-chih8 be7 tin2-tang7 . Hong3-kiam iu7-koh siong5-siong5 tu2-tioh8 chok-giat8 e5 gin2-na2, a2-si7 bo5 thian-liong5 e5 ok-han3 beh khi-hu7. Ai5--ah! Tai7-ke chaiN2-iuN7 m7-tioh8 ai3 pun5-khui3? 
  3. Kiu3-keng3 si7 bo5 thak8 bo5 ka3 sou2 ti3--e5 
  Tai7-ke hian7-si5 e5 cho-gu7, kiu3-keng3 siuN7-chin , si7 in-ui7 ku2-ni5 kau3-hoa3 bo5 heng, sit-liau2 ka3-si7 sou2 ti3--e5, hou7 kau3-hoa3 chiah-nih8 soe-the3 e5 goan5-in sng3-lai5 si7 chin-che7. Hoat-tou7 siat-liau2 m7-ho2 ia7 si7 u7 , iah8 u7 chit8-pou7 e5 lang5 ai3 cheng3-lang5 gong7, ka-ti7 thang choan-koan5, iong7 chiong2-chiong2 e5 chhiu2-toaN7 teh chou2-gai7 ia7 si7 u7. Chong2-si7 choe3-toa7 e5 goan5-in si7 chai7 cheng3-lang5 be7-hiau2 kau3-iok8 e5 po2-poe3 , kan-ta ui7-tioh8 bak8-cheng5 e5 chiah8-png7 chhut-lat8, khoaN3 thak8-chheh kang2-kiu3 e5 su7 cho3 ke--e5, liah8-cho3 si7 khang-liau2 kang. 
  Lan2 pun2-lai5 e5 seng3-chit si7 khah ti3-tiong7 sit8-chai7 , khah kou3 bak8-chiu-cheng5; ban7-hang7 to si7 ai3 chin-tu2-chin sit8-tu2-sit8 , long2 si7 tiong7 iat-lek8, tou2 thian-un7 na7-tiaN7 . Khah che7 si7 sin3, kong2 , lang5 beh chiuN7-koan5 chhut-sin m7-bian2 tek-khak ai3 thak8-chheh; sou2-i2 u7 chit8-ku3 oe7 kong2 , “Liu5 Hang7 goan5-lai5 si7 put thok8-su.” Si7 kong2 Han3-tiau5 e5 khai-ki-chu2 Lau5 Pang kap Chhou2 Pa3-ong5 Hang7 U2 ; chit poe3 e5 lang5 long2 bo5 thak8-chheh, in to ia7 e7 peh hiah koan5 , cho3 hiah toa7 e5 tai7-chi3, Che si7 kou2-cha2 e5 su7-chek, ti7 cheng3 lang5 long2 si7 gu5-gong7 m7-bat sim2-mih8 e5 si5-tai7 , kiam2-chhai2 e7 iong7-tit ; chai7 kin-a2-jit8 ban7-it na7-si7 iau2-ku2 u7 lang5 an2-ni sin3 , chiu7-si7 chin kho2-lin5. Si5-tai7 i2-keng bo5 sio-siang7, hian7-si5 si7 hak8-bun7 e5 si5-tai7, kin7-kin7 iong7 chit8-lang7 e5 iat-lek8 keng-giam7 si7 toan3-jian5 be7 thang cho3 sim2-mih8, sit8-chai7 si7 oh-tit khia7 e7-chai7 thang koe3-jit8.. 
  Khah-cha2 si7 ko3-jin5 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7, ban7-su7 long2 si7 tui3 ka-ti7 chit8-lang5 lai5 phah-sng3, long2 si7 chit8-lang5 tui3 chit8-lang5 e5 cho3-hoat ; sou2-i2 khah che7 tioh8 pin5 chu7-ki2 e5 khui3-lat8 ; iong7 ka-ti7 e5 chu2-koat choan-toan3. Phi3-lun7 tui3 cho3 seng-li2 e5 hong-bin7 kong2, khah-cha2 long2 si7 chit8-lang5 chit8-lang5 ka-ti7 cho3, tak8-hang7 chin kan2-tan , kok-lang5 e5 khui3-lat8 to si7 u7 han7-liong7 , sou2-i2 chit8-lang5 tu2 chit8-lang5 e5 su-iaN5 cheng-chha si7 bo5 loa7-che7. Hian7-si5 i2-keng m7-si7 chit-khoan2 e5 cho3-hoat; hian7-si5 si7 kiong7-tong5 hiap8-lek8 e5 si5-tai7, sou2-i2 seng-li2 ia7 si7 hap8 cheng3-lang5 e5 khui3-lat8 teh cho3. Li2 khoaN3, hian7-si5 u7 ke chin-che7 khoan2 e5 sin ki-koan , u7 kio3-cho3 sim2-mih8 hoe7-sia7 , sim2-mih8 gin5-hang5 , long2 si7 iong7 tu-sek hap8 che7-che7 kou2-tu teh cho3, pun2-chiN5 si7 chin-chiaN3 toa7, seng-li2 si7 cho3 hui-siong5 khoah, i e5 khui3-lat8 bo5 han7-liong7 . Siok8-gu2 kong2, “Sio-kap bi2 , chu2 u7 chhun.” In-ui7 pun2 toa7 , siau-lou7 toa7 , sou2-i2 mih8-kiaN7 oe7-thang teng2-chin koh-chai3 siok8 . M7-na7 an2-ni , iau2-ku2 oe7-thang an-pai5 i e5 tiam3-lai7 chin sui2 , e7 giu2 lang5-kheh e5 bak8-chiu , ia7 oe7-thang siat-pi7 che7-che7 hang7 hou7 lang5-kheh hoaN-hi2. 
  Goa2 e5 bak8-chiu sou2 u7 chhin khoaN3-kiN3 siang7-toa7 kham2 e5 bun5-chhi7 seng-li2-tiam3, kan-ta hit-keng tiam3 e5 chhu3, si7 khi2 si3 gou7 pah-ban7 gin5, si7 lak8 chan3 e5 iuN5-lau5 , lai7-bin7 e5 phou-siat oan2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 ong5-kiong, tiam3-lai7 toa7-sio2 e5 hoe2-ki3 ta-pou cha-bou2 chong2-kiong7 chheng-goa7 lang5. Lai7-bin7 u7 i2 thang hou7 lang5-kheh the-to2, ia7 chin-che7 cha-bou2-gin2-na2 teh phang5-te5 , ia7 u7 hoe-hng5 thang hou7 lang5-kheh siong2-goan2, ia7 u7 lang5 teh chau3-gak8 cho3-hi3 hou7 lang5-kheh thiaN khoaN3. Iah8 lang5-kheh na7 pak-tou2 iau ia7 u7 thang hou7 i be2-chiah8 , m7-bian2 koh chau2 khi3 pat8-tah. Na7 joah8 e5 si5 u7 thang chhit-bin7 ia7 tian7-hong thang liang5, lang5-kheh e5 saN eng-soa u7 lang5 thang ka7 i chhit. Lang5-kheh sou2-be2 e5 mih8 m7-bian2 ka-ti7 theh8 , na7 ka7 i kau-tai3 , u7 chu7-tong7-chhia a2-si7 hoe2-chhia thang ka7 lang5 chai3 kau3 chhu3. Na7-si7 khah-hng7--e5 , sui5-si5 oe7-thang ka7 lan2 kia3 iu5-pian7 un7-sang3 kau3 lan2 tau; put-lun7 li2 kau-koan che7-chio2 to long2 si7 chit-khoan2 e5 saN khoan2-thai7. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit-khoan2 e5 cho3-hoat, chit8-lang5 e5 sio2 seng-li2 beh tong3 thai3-e7 thang chai7, tiaN7-tioh8 ai3 to2-tiam3! Chong2-si7 chit-ho7 seng-li2 m7-si7 hoah-cho3 chiu7 sui5-si5 oe7-thang-cho3 , tioh8 bat chin-che7 hong-bin7 e5 tai7-chi3, tioh8 hap8 chin-che7 lang5 e5 ti3-sek, chiah cho3 oe7-thang lai5. Chit-khoan2 si7 chin-che7 lang5 saN-kap iok-sok teh cho3, sou2-i2 tek-khak tioh8 u7 cheng2-cheng2 e5 kui-ki2 , tioh8 beng5-pek8 hoat-lut8 chiah cho3 e7 thang si3-chiaN3. 
  Iu7-koh kau-koan si7 chin khoah , hang5-cheng5 ai3 cheng-thong , chu7-jian5 phoe-sin3 oan2-lai5 si7 chin chiap8, sou2-i2 m7-na7 ka-ti7 e5 bun5-ji7 tioh8 ai3 bat, pat8 kok e5 oe7 kap bun5 to long2 ai3 cheng-thong. Siau3-bak8 chin-che7 chin chap8, tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 ki3 chiah e7 beng5-pek8, chiN5-gin5 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 un7-choan2 chiah e7 liu5-thong , tiam3-lai7 e5 sou2-hui3 tioh8 an2-choaN2 iong7 chiah e7 chiat-iok, che ia7 m7-si7 chit8 lang5 sou2 siuN7 e7 kau3 . Tui3 chit kui2 tiam2 siuN7 ia7 chiu7 thang chai, hian7-chai7 beh cho3 seng-li2 , tioh8 ai3 u7 hak8-bun7 tioh8 thak8-chheh, tioh8 chai-iaN2 che7-che7 gau5-lang5 sou2 keng-giam7 sou2 iat-lek8 sou2 gian2-kiu3 e5 kiat-ko2 , chiong hiah-e5 theh8 lai5 cho3 chham-kho2, an2-ni hian7-si5 e5 seng-li2 chiah cho3 e7 lai5 , ia7 chiah e7 seng5-kong. Cho3 seng-li2 i2-goa7 bo5-lun7 si7 choh-sit8, a2-si7 cho3 kang , chai7 hian7-si5 to long2 tioh8 thak8-chheh, u7 hak8-bun7, chiah e7 thang kap lang5 peN5 che7 khia7. 
  Lun7 lang5 thak8-chheh gian2-kiu3 hak8-bun7 u7 nng7-khoan2 e5 bok8-tek. Chit8 khoan2 si7 beh hou7 lang5 e5 phin2-seng3 chiau5-chng5 , koh chit8 hang7 si7 beh hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 cho3-kang pan7-su7 e5 chai5-leng5. Beng7 Hu-chu2 kong2, “Thak8-chheh bo5 pat8-hang7 , kan-ta si7 beh kiu5 sou2 phah-m7-kiN3e5 liong5-sim to3-tng2-lai5”, chiu7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 e5 phin2-seng3 chiau5-chng5 e5 i3-su3, che si7 thak8-chheh te7-it e5 bok8-tek. Chong2-si7 khah che7 lang5 bo5 siuN7 kau3 chit-tiam2, kong2 thak8-chheh si7 beh than3-chiN5 , cho3 koaN . Than3-chiN5 , cho3 koaN , cho3 tai7-chi3 , che si7 siok8 ki-sut8 chai5-leng5 e5 hong-bin7, si7 thak8-chheh kang2-kiu3 hak8-bun7 te7-ji7 e5 bok8-tek, khah-cha2 si7 kan-ta khoaN3 tang7 ti7 chit-tiam2, che si7 khah phian e5 khoaN3-hoat. Lang5 kan-ta hou7 lau7-bo2 seN--chhut-lai5 si7 bo5 chiau5-chng5 , si7 chit8 e5 lang5 e5 chhou-phoe na7-tiaN7 , tek-khak tioh8 koh kang2-kiu3 hak8-bun7 , chai-iaN2 chin-che7 gau5-lang5 e5 sou2 siuN7 sou2 kiaN5, thang hou7 lan2 e5 thau5-nau2 oah8-tang7 sim-su beng5-pek8, hou7 lan2 e7-hiau2 cho3 kang pan7-su7 e5 hoat-tou7, khi2-thau5 chiah e7 sng3-tit si7 chiau5-chng5. Chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 chiong5-chian5 kau3-iok8 long2 bo5 heng, hak8-bun7 long2 sit-tui7, che long2 si7 tui3 lan2 tai7-ke ka-ti7 kap lan2 e5 chou2-sian khah che7 bo5 beng5-pek8 hak8-bun7 e5 chin i3-gi7 , be7 hiau2-tit si5-se3 e5 pian3-chhian sou2 ti3--e5. 
  Liat8 ui7 hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 , si5-se3 i2-keng pian3-oaN7 liau2 .Khah-cha2 si7 chit8-lang5 tui3 chit8-lang5 teh cho3-su7 , si7 ko3-jin5 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7, hian7-kim si7 cheng3-lang5 tui3 cheng3-lang5 , thoan5-the2 tui3 thoan5-the2, si7 hiap8-tong5 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7 . Khah-cha2 si7 chit8-lang5 gau5 , cheng3-lang5 gong7 ; chit8-lang5 ti3-im3 cheng3-lang5 , chit8-lang5 hou-hat cheng3-lang5;si7 eng-hiong5 chu2-gi7 , si7 choan-che3 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7; hian7-kim si cheng3-lang5 gau5, cheng3-lang5 iong2;kong-ke cho3, kong-ke siu, iong7 che7 lang5 e5 ho2, che3-chi2 cheng3-lang5 e5 phaiN2 , si7 bin5-chiong3 chu2-gi7, bin5-pun2 chu2-gi e5 si5-tai7.Khah cha2 si7 sui5-pian7 ai3, sui5-pian7 thang cho3, kok lang5 oe7-thang phah kok-lang5 e5 sng3 , si chu7-jian5 chu3-gi hong3-jim7 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7; hian7-kim si7 u7 jin7-teng7 chit8 e5 kong-ke e5 phiau-chun2, kong-ke e5 kui-ki2 , kong-ke tioh8 ai3 siu2;chiu7-si7 li2-siong2 chu2-gi, hoat-ti7 chu2-gi7 e5 si5-tai7. Chong2-kong2 chit8 ku3, cha2-cheng5 si7 chit8-lang5 chit8-lang5 ka-ti7 oah8 e5 cho3-hoat; hian7-kim si7 pian3-chiaN5 chit8-lang5 hap8 cheng3-lang5, cho3-hoe2 oah8 e5 cho3-hoat.Thang chai chai7 hian7-kim e5 si5-se3, chit8-lang5 kap cheng3-lang5 si7 chin toa7 u7 koan-he7, sou2-i chit8-lang5 be7-thang chiau3 ka-ti7 e5 phah-sng3, tioh8 chai-iaN2 cheng3-lang5 e5 tai7-chi3 ; tioh8 bat chin khoah, sou2-i2 tioh8 u7 hak8-bun7, u7 ti3-sek chiah e7 eng7-tit.TaN lan2 tai7-ke chai, lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kiam2 m7-si7 bak8-chiu long2 m7-bat “It--ji7” si7 chit8-oeh8 mah? Iah8 ta-pou-lang5 kui2 lang5 u7 thak8-chheh neh? Ai5--ah! Si5-se3 pian3 liau2-liau2! Lan2 tai7-ke iau2-ku2 si7 bak8-chiu ou-am3--e5 khah che7.An2-ni khoaN3, tai7-ke chaiN2-iuN7 m7-bian2 kan-khou2 e7 eng7-tit! Lan2 sit8-chai7 si7 sit ka3-si7, lan2 e5 thau5-khak-oaN2 lai7 si7 long2 khang-khang.Tai5-oan5 hian7-kim si7 chai7 ti3-sek ki-hng e5 si5-chun7 lah! 
  4.TaN tioh8 kin2-kin2 phou2-kip8 lo5-ma2-ji7
  Se3-kan khek-khek teh oaN7-sin, si5-se3 i2-keng pian3-oaN7 liau2, chong2-si7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 Pun2-to2 lang5, hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7, iau2-ku2 si7 chiau3 ku7-khoan2, be7-thang eng3 si5-se3.Che si7 in-ui7 sit kau3-iok8 bo5 hak8-bun7 sou2 ti3--e5; lan2 i2-keng beng5-pek8 liau2.TaN lan2 tioh8 koaN2-kin2 lai5 chin2-heng lan2 e5 kau3-iok8.Lun7 chit hang7 kau3-iok8 e5 tai7-chi3, m7-si7 chit8-si5 chit8-khek sou2 cho3 oe7-thang lai5, tioh8 ai3 chin-ku2 e5 khou2-sim, chiah chit8-sut-a2 e7-tit kian3 kong-hau7.Jit8-pun2 Te3-kok leng2 Tai5 i2-cheng5, siu7 chu-pang5 ku7-sek e5 kau3-iok8 bat Han3-bun5 Han3-hak8 e5 lang5 si7 bo5 loa7-che7. Hian7-kim m7-chai iau2 chhun u7 chap8-ban7 lang5 a2-bo5? Goa2 teh giau5-gi5.Chu7 leng2 Tai5 i2-au7, Chong2-tok-hu2 u7 sin-siat cheng2-cheng2 e5 hak8-hau7;kau3-taN siu7 chit khoan2 kau3-iok8, oh8 sin hak8-bun7 e5 lang5, chhim-chhian2 bo5-lun7 it-chhe3 sng3 chai7-lai7, ia7 kaN2 bo5 thang chiuN7 chap8-ban7, che-si7 goa2 e5 chhui-siong2 phah-sng3 kaN2-bo5 siuN toa7 cheng-chha.Pun2-to2 lang5 long2-kiong7 u7 saN-pah lak8-chap8-ban7 lang5, kin7-kin7 chiah chha-put-to ji7-chap8-ban7 lang5 u7 hak8-bun7, kiam2 m7-si7 chin chio2 mah? Che si7 sim2-mih8 goan5-in neh? Chit8 hang7, si7 lan2 ka-ti7 be7-hiau2 khoaN3 hak8-bun7 tang7;chit8 hang7, si7 siat-hoat e5 lang5 bo5 u7 chap8-hun e5 seng5-sim.Iau2 koh chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 beh oh8 hak8-bun7 e5 bun5-ji7 gian5-gu2 thai3 kan-ke3 hui-siong5 oh-tit oh8. 
  Tu2-tioh8 hian7-si5 e5 keng2-hong2, chhu2-khi3 tai7-ke tek-khak tui3 kau3-iok8 e7 chin jiat8-sim chiah tioh8.Tan7-si7 chit8 hang7 bun5-ji7 kap gian5-gu2 tioh8 koh chit8 hoan e5 toa7 chhim-siuN7 toa7 gian2-kiu3.Tai5-oan5 kap Tiong-kok e5 ong2-lai5 tek-khak be7 eng7-tit keh-tng7 khi3, sou2-i2 Han3-bun5 si7 toan3-toan3 be7 eng7-tit pang3-sak.Tai5-oan5 lang5 iu7 si7 Jit8-pun2 e5 peh-seN3, sou2-i2 Jit8-pun2 e5 Kok-gu2 ia7-si7 tek-khak tioh8 ai3 oh8. M7-ku2 Han3-bun5 si7 chin oh, Kok-gu2 ia7 si7 chin lan5, koh-chai3 chit nng7 hang7 kap Tai5-oan5-oe7 long2 si7 bo5 koan-he7.chit8 e5 lang5 beh sio2-khoa2 cheng-thong chit nng7 khoan2 gian5-gu2 bun5-ji7, chi3-chio2 tioh8 ai3 chap8-ni5 e5 kang-hu;thang kong2 si7 chin tang7 e5 taN3-thau5.Siau3-lian5 gin2-na2 chu7 se3-han3 oh8-khi2 , chiu7 u7 ng3-bang7 e7 seng5-kong;hian7-si5 m7-bat ji7 e5 toa7-lang5 beh lai5 oh8.phah-sng3 oh8 kau3 si2 ia7 kaN2-si7 be7-chiaN5. 
  Hian7-kim chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 eng-kai khi3 hak8-hau7 thak8-chheh e5 siau3-lian5 gin2-na2, peng5-kin chit8 pah lang5 tiong chiah saN-chap8-saN lang5 khi3 thak8-chheh;au7-chhiu2 lak8-chap8 chhit lang5 si7 tioh8 cho3 bo5 hak8-bun7 e5 kha-siau3.Thang chai, hian7-kim chai7 Tai5-oan5 e5 gin2-na2 saN-hun7 nng7 si7 iau2 bo5 hak8-hau7 thang thak8-chheh, kiam2 m7-si7 chin kho2-lin5 mah? Na7 kong2 kau3 ji7-chap8 hoe3, saN-chap8 hoe3 i2-siong7 e5 ta-pou cha-bou2 , bo5 ki-hoe7 thang chiap-kin7 hak8-hau7--e5 si7 moa2-si3-ke3.Chiah e5 ji7, saN-chap8 hoe3 i2-siong7 e5 lang5, chiaN3-chiaN3 si7 teh keng-eng5 hian7-kim e5 Tai5-oan5.Chiah-e5 m7-bat hak8-bun7 m7-bat tai7-chi3, Tai5-oan5 beh thai3 e7 oaN7-sin chin3-pou7? Iah8 chit-chun7 e5 siau3-lian5 gin2-na2 si7 au7-tai7 beh keng-eng5 Tai5-oan5 e5 jin5-chai5, chiah-e5 chit-chun7 bo5 hak8-hau7 thang thak8-chheh, au7-lai5 beh-thai3 u7 lou7-eng7? An2-ni Tai5-oan5 beh-thai3 u7 hiong3-siong7 e5 jit8, lan2 beh thai3 u7 chhut-thau5-thiN e5 si5? Kau3 chia sng3 si7 chui2 kek kau3 phiN7-khang-khau2, lan2 bo5 jin7-chin lai5 siat-hoat chaiN2-iuN7 e7 eng7-tit? 
  Chit e5 bun7-te5 goa2 chu7 chap8-goa7 ni5 cheng5 chiu7 u7 se3-se3 siuN7-koe3 liau2.Chiau3 goa2 e5 sou2 siuN7, goa2 sin3 kong2, na7 m7-si7 kin2-kin2 phou2-kip8 lo5-ma2-ji7 si7 bo5 pian3.Tai7-cheng3 saN-ni5 e5 ni5-boe2, Pan2-hoan5 Pek-chiok tui3 Tang-kiaN lai5 lan2 Tai5-oan5, kap Lim5 Hian3-tong5 Sian-seN i2-goa7 chin-che7 lang5, hiap8-lek8 beh chhong3-siat Tong5-hoa3-hoe7 e5 si5, goa2 ti7 hit-si5 chiu7 u7 tui3 in kian3-gi7 tioh8 chhai2-iong7 Lo5-ma2-ji7.Hit-si5 in tui3 goa2 kong2, “Chong2-tok-hu2 kap chin-che7 Loe7-te7-lang5 tui3 chit e5 hoe7 put-chi2 toa7 hoan2-tui3; chim2-ma2 na7 kong2 beh phou2-kip8 Lo5-ma2-ji7, thang chhiok-chin3 Tai5-oan5 e5 kau3-iok8, kiaN-liau2 e7 koh-khah hoan2-tui3.” Chiau3 in tai7-ke hit-si5 e5 i3-su3, si7 kong2 siat Tong5-hoa3-hoe7 si7 beh hou7 Pun2-to2-lang5 tong5-hoa3 kap Loe7-te7-lang5 siang7-khoan2, sou2-i2 tai7-ke tioh8 jiat8-sim oh8 Kok-gu2 chiah ho2; chim2-ma2 na7-si7 lai5 ka3 Lo5-ma2-ji7, beh eng7 Tai5-oan5-oe7 lai5 ka3 Pun2-to2 lang5 e5 hak8-bun7, Chong2-tok-hu2 tek-khak e7 kong2, che si7 beh kio3 Pun2-to3-lang5 tui3 Kok-gu2 na2 bo5 jiat8-sim, na2 kap Loe7-te7-lang5 li7-khui, sou2-i2 Chong2-tok-hu2 tek-khak e7 koh-khah hoan2-tui3. 
  Hit-si5 goa2 u7 siong5-se3 pian7-beng5 hou7 in thiaN, chong2-si7 to bo5 chhai2-kang.Chiau3 goa2 hit-si5 sou2 siuN7, Pun2-to2 lang5 kap Loe7-te7 lang5 hoa3-cho3 sio-siang7-khoan2 si7 ho2, chong2-si7 bo5 tek-khak Pun2-to2 lang5 long2 tioh8 hoa3 chiu7-kin7 Loe7-te7-lang5. Pun2-to2 lang5 u7 phaiN2-e5 hoa3 chiu7-kin7 Loe7-te7 lang5 e5 ho2, che-si7 e7 eng7-tit; m7-ku2 Pun2-to2-lang5 u7 ho2-e5, ia7 tioh8 hoa3-khi3 chiu7-kin7 Loe7-te7-lang5 e5 phaiN2-e5, che-si7 toan3-toan3 be7-eng7-tit. Put-ko3 u7 ho2 saN-kap oh8 , u7 phaiN2 saN-kap tu2; tai7-ke long2 lai5 saN-kap piN3-cho3 ho2, che chiah si7 chin-chiaN3 e5 tong5-hoa3. Sou2-i2 tai7-ke tioh8 ai3 tai7-seng e7-hiau2 ho2-phaiN2 si7 sim2-mih8 , tai7-seng u7 siang7-khoan2 e5 ti3-sek si7 iau3-kin2. Tai7-ke jiat8-sim oh8 Kok-gu2 ia7-si7 ho2, m7-ku2 kio3 hian7-si5 ji7-saN-chap8-hoe3 i2-siong7 e5 lang5 tioh8 seng oh8 Kok-gu2, jian5-au7 tui3 Kok-gu2 chiah lai5 oh8 ti3-sek, an2-ni si7 bo5 ng3-bang7 e5 tai7-chi3. Hiah e5 lang5 kau3-si2 phah-sng3 Kok-gu2 ia7-si7 oh8 be7-chiaN5 . Sou2-i2 tek-khak tioh8 kin2-kin2 seng ka3 Lo5-ma2-ji7 chiah tioh8. Che-si7 goa2 hit-si5 e5 i3-kian3. 
